" RAP Service Binding — OData V4 (new mandatory approach)
" Type: OData V4 - UI  (not V2)
" Replaces SEGW-based OData V2 gateway development

" CDS View with Fiori Elements UI Annotations
@UI.headerInfo: { typeName: 'Sales Order',
                   typeNamePlural: 'Sales Orders',
                   title.value: 'OrderId' }
define root view entity ZI_SalesOrder
  as select from zsales_order
{
  @UI.lineItem:  [{ position: 10 }]
  @UI.selectionField: [{ position: 10 }]
  key order_id       as OrderId,
  @UI.lineItem:  [{ position: 20 }]
      customer_id    as CustomerId,
  @UI.lineItem:  [{ position: 30 }]
      total_amount   as TotalAmount,
      status         as Status
}
" Result: Fiori List Report auto-generated — zero JS code needed

